  {
    "type": "EXPOSITORY (ENGLISH BIBLE)",
    "name": "Gill's Exposition of the Entire Bible",
    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "And now I have sent a cunning man, endued with understanding,.... In such things as Solomon required he should, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "2 Chronicles 2:7",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "of Huram my father's; a workman of his, whom he employed, and so might be depended upon as a good artificer; though rather Huram is the artificer's name: ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "and Abi, we render \"my father\", his surname, that is, \"Huram Abi\"; and this is the opinion of several learned men (g), and is very probable; for certain it is, that his name was Huram or Hiram, 1 Kings 7:13, and so he is called \"Huram his father, or Huram Abif\", 2 Chronicles 4:16. ",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "and Abi, we render \"my father\", his surname, that is, \"Huram Abi\"; and this is the opinion of several learned men (g), and is very probable; for certain it is, that his name was Huram or Hiram, ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "1 Kings 7:13",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": ", and so he is called \"Huram his father, or Huram Abif\", ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "2 Chronicles 4:16",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": ". ",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "(g) Luther. Emanuel Sa, Piscator, Schmidt, Beckius in Targum in loc. ",
